========================================================================
* Luu y khi su dung VPSSIM:
========================================================================
* Neu Server ho tro tao SWAP, ban nen su dung chuc nang [Quan ly SWAP]
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* de tao SWAP, nang cao hieu suat Server.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* De an toan, neu co su co xay ra ban van co the phuc hoi duoc website
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Ban nen bat chuc nang Auto Backup code va Auto Backup Database.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Auto Backup Code: 
------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
* VPSSIM menu => Backup & Restore Code => Auto Backup (ALL) Website
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Auto Backup Database: 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* VPSSIM menu => Quan ly Database ==> Auto Backup (ALL) Database
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Hoac su dung chuc nang: 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* 1. Quan Ly Resilio Sync de Auto backup du lieu ve may tinh cua minh.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* 2. Quan Ly VPS Backup de Auto backup du lieu sang server khac.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* 3. Backup VPS To Google Drive
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Voi Wordpress Website: Ban co the bao ve wp-login.php bang chuc nang:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* VPSSIM menu ==> Wordpress Blog Tools ==> Password Bao Ve wp-login.php
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Voi nhung code khac, Bao ve Folder bang chuc nang:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* VPSSIM menu ==> Bao Mat Server & Website ==> Dat Mat Khau Bao Ve Folder
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* De tranh SSH scan port, ban nen doi SSH port bang chuc nang: 
------------------------------------------------------------------------
* VPSSIM menu ==> Bao Mat Server & Website ==> Thay Doi Port SSH Number

------------   http://vpssim.vn && http://vpssim.com   -----------------


